        "Update all Delete/Move/Copy click-behavior tests (lines 202-460) — each needs to open dropdown first before clicking the action button",
        "Add new tests for: vertical-dots button visibility on hover, right-click context menu, alignment"
      ]
    },
    {
      "test_file": "src/app.characterization.test.ts",
      "changes_needed": [
        "Update header assertion (line 232) — remove 'Actions' header",
