        "Update 'makeParentRow has four cells' (lines 459-464) — may change to 3 cells, or 4th cell may no longer be empty",
        "Update 'makeActionButton' section (lines 404-442) — buttons may have different classes/attributes inside dropdown",
        "Update Download anchor attributes test (lines 419-431) — find inside dropdown",
        "Update folder no-Download test (lines 434-442) — find inside dropdown"
      ]
    },
    {
      "test_file": "src/app/render-orchestration.test.ts",
      "changes_needed": [
        "Update header assertions (lines 177, 209) — remove 'Actions' from expected headers"
      ]
    },
    {
      "test_file": "src/app/render-browse.ts",
      "changes_needed": "The buildTable call (line 30) passes ['Name', 'Size', 'Modified', 'Actions'] as headers. The Actions header may be removed or replaced."
    },
    {
      "test_file": "src/app/dom-builders.ts",
